                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                        We define target metrics with you, like activation, task success, completion time, NPS, or support tickets. We track usability findings, A/B results, and adoption. Dashboards show trend lines. Each release includes a short readout covering what improved, what needs work, and next experiments to keep momentum. Results guide priorities.

                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
