                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                        Our process is simple: kickoff, research, and problem framing; sketches and flows; wireframes and content; visual exploration and design system; interactive prototypes and testing; then handoff and QA. We keep cycles short, share progress early, and document decisions so engineering can build confidently and efficiently. Teams stay closely aligned. Throughout.
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
