                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <ul>
                                    <li> We support AEST, ACST, and AWST. We plan standing touchpoints that fall within your team’s working hours, and we share updates asynchronously for others. Critical reviews, usability sessions, and handoffs are scheduled to accommodate participants across time zones so decisions are quick and no one is left behind. Always.</li>

                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
