                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingSeven">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed p-2" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseSeven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseThree">
                                Can you meet in person in major Australian cities?

                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="flush-collapseSeven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingSeven" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                        Yes. We can arrange onsite workshops or stakeholder sessions in Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane, Perth, Adelaide, and Canberra. For discovery, testing, or roadmapping, we combine in-person sessions with remote research to keep momentum. Travel is scoped upfront so you have clear timelines, costs, and deliverables before we begin. When appropriate.

